imdb.plot outline: The epic FBI solve some of the most unknown mysteries in the entire town of Jimmtown. They are now recording all of the epic mysteries that they have solved. This leads you to this show as you watch Xander Yogret (not his real last name), Brodie, and Jonny go through their adventure in the Epic FBI.
